tasks.description:
Supabase MCP를 사용해 4개의 마이그레이션을 순서대로 적용한다.

마이그레이션 1: create_events_table
- CREATE TYPE event_status AS ENUM('draft','open','closed','cancelled');
- CREATE TABLE events (id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY, group_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES groups(id) ON DELETE CASCADE, title TEXT NOT NULL, description TEXT, location TEXT, event_date TIMESTAMPTZ, max_participants INT, status event_status NOT NULL DEFAULT 'open', created_by UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES auth.users(id), created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now());
- CREATE INDEX idx_events_group_id ON events(group_id);
- ALTER TABLE events ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

마이그레이션 2: create_event_participants_table
- CREATE TYPE participant_status AS ENUM('attending','declined','maybe','waitlisted');
- CREATE TABLE event_participants (id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY, event_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES events(id) ON DELETE CASCADE, user_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES auth.users(id), status participant_status NOT NULL, waitlist_position INT, UNIQUE(event_id, user_id));
- CREATE INDEX idx_event_participants_event_id ON event_participants(event_id);
- ALTER TABLE event_participants ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

마이그레이션 3: create_events_rls_policies
- events SELECT: auth.uid() IS NOT NULL AND is_group_member(group_id)
- events INSERT: auth.uid() IS NOT NULL AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM group_members WHERE group_id = events.group_id AND user_id = auth.uid() AND role IN ('owner','admin'))
- events UPDATE/DELETE: auth.uid() IS NOT NULL AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM group_members WHERE group_id = events.group_id AND user_id = auth.uid() AND role IN ('owner','admin'))
- event_participants SELECT: auth.uid() IS NOT NULL AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM events e WHERE e.id = event_participants.event_id AND is_group_member(e.group_id))
- event_participants INSERT/UPDATE: auth.uid() = user_id
- event_participants DELETE: auth.uid() = user_id

마이그레이션 4: supabase gen types typescript로 types/supabase.ts 재생성
(Supabase MCP generate_typescript_types 도구 사용)

5. ROADMAP_V1.md DB 마이그레이션 체크박스 4개 체크

